There are two ways to perceive the Dharmaï¼š the Sudden Way, the way in which
the obstacle of illusion is shattered by a striking awareness; and the
Gradual Way, the way in which illusion is dispelled incrementally, by
continuous effort. One way or the other the obstacle must be destroyed.
